data.description: This beautiful home, built in 2022 with over 2,300 sq. feet is BETTER than new construction & features 3 spacious bedrooms PLUS a main floor office which could be 4th bedroom AND a HUGE loft.  The main floor also features stunning floors, an open concept kitchen w/quartz counters, stainless steel appliances & walk-in pantry.  Elegant, spacious living room w/fireplace, dining w/sliding doors to fully fenced yard & half bath. Upstairs an enormous loft, primary bedroom w/huge walk-in closet & spacious bath plus 2 more bedrooms, laundry & full bath. Beautiful front & backyard, new fence, Air-conditioning.  Minutes to restaurants, shopping, easy access to JBLM.  Assumable VA Loan 4.625 interest rate, 3,218.37 total monthly payment!!
